      <title>交易员押注降息，美国国债抹去 2024 年的损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/treasuries-wipe-out-this-year-s-loss-as-traders-bet-on-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于通胀降温增强了对美联储降息的押注，美国国债已经抹去了今年的跌幅，投资者目前转向生产者价格来确认通货紧缩趋势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/treasuries-wipe-out-this-year-s-loss-as-traders-bet-on-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 05:06:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
